headline: 3 Internet Delivery Services Stocks in Focus Amid Industry Challenges
summary: Tariff war, inflationary pressure and still-high interest rates are major concerns for the Zacks Internet - Delivery Services industry. However, efforts to adopt consumer preferences and technological advancements are likely to help GDDY, QNST and ASUR navigate the headwinds.
